data.title: Freiburg Weather Forecast, Germany
data.meta_description: Weather in Freiburg for today, tomorrow and 25 day weather forecast for Freiburg.
data.text: Weather now in Freiburg is 27C (81F) and clear. Tomorrow it will be 17C (63F). The next weekend it will be 17C (63F) on Saturday and 19C (66F) on Sunday. Read more The warmest day over the next 26 days weather in Freiburg is forecast to be Thursday 29th August 2024 at 23C (73F) and the warmest night on Saturday 7th September 2024 at 18C (64F). The average temperature over the next 26 days in Freiburg from this forecast is 16C (60F) and there will be 5 days of sunshine .
